"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641407638,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"mmUJ5HNZVL-pcSZtqINuaGqda_3Ct7pgLzNBZ3oYmQo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x765759011df2A2ffE092159d66f89d677E707a74\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"BNrsyRXe6lmVtT4E4LzosPM1qbaK9v_SYg3puHiCggc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VLsDn8lrB-YcR_RwrwMDQxjkWnRFRX4W7sNewauHOJA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lfo0EGYJR5appY0-wA9pB4ltsaSCxIzwmHtYEiv3jKjmsMYxGep_KR3o0aCSMFoOGUSiIbepUaCXyEIioVTTgg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6786c35fae76c7d9e0eb0ffd3af49ccdd15464abbd5931d994271ebf073aafbe53aad4c5aa43d81b05f3c6c07224440741e95e22fffda934e0952fe01d17f5bb1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"BNrsyRXe6lmVtT4E4LzosPM1qbaK9v_SYg3puHiCggc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VLsDn8lrB-YcR_RwrwMDQxjkWnRFRX4W7sNewauHOJA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi